Add `^anchor` syntax for anchors. Supports linking to blocks with `[[link text|tiddler title^anchor]]`, single block transclusion with `{{Title^anchor}}`, range transclusion with `{{Title^start..^end}}`, block-level backlinks with `[backlinks:anchor[anchor]]`, and code anchors with closing fence syntax ` ``` ^anchor`. The anchor becomes a container widget wrapping the target block, enabling plugin developers to build advanced deep reference features.
